# Title: File Deletion
# Author: Ömer Günal, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-07
# Level: informational
# Description: Detects file deletion using "rm", "shred" or "unlink" commands which are used often by adversaries to delete files left behind by the actions of their intrusion activity
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1070.004
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/process_creation/proc_creation_lnx_file_deletion.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate administration activities

Image IN ("*/rm", "*/shred", "*/unlink")